{"tid":788710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線巴士阿叔","createTime":"2018-08-21T16:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T16:44:35.000Z","uid":36728,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8ff62a480d41b39deee77769282ef5f2038596","tid":788710,"uid":36728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"小妹啱啱係銅鑼灣搭969翻屋企，準備係麗湖居落車，落樓梯果陣聽到道門就關，男朋友落左車，我開口講唔好關住，司機仲要同我理論，話小姐你幾時決定落車，點解人地落到你落唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 我:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">甘你俾唔俾我落？</span><br />\n司機:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">甘你幾時決定落車</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我話遲左幾秒姐，佢俾我落車之後仲要開前門鬧7我話：閉路影住你咖</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我都好想睇閉路究竟我係遲左幾多落車</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好間車行緊就全部起身係門後面排定隊等出，唔好要司機要你甘耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要報警</span>"},{"pid":"4549a36693e7d093fda1b9b54ae7961ebf262956","tid":788710,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"點解你唔去做雞仆街死"},{"pid":"3fab9f44d1c597279abf90d4add130730bf3aed9","tid":788710,"uid":172485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"報囉 <br />\n甘你老母"},{"pid":"a65e0d1a38f19d0fba1342419bf51075f0462317","tid":788710,"uid":202638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"又一個西客✌🏻"},{"pid":"474905e0b2c61167f402418b4f066d9f641b9226","tid":788710,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"文盲係會蝕底啲㗎喇"},{"pid":"b161579e5529c832c60a0c60668e1cd34745a220","tid":788710,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/003658_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F003658_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a61f811a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0997c5a00fcaf40445b7ee017236d67a196e5215","tid":788710,"uid":190739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"係你男友唔啱，自己一個落車唔等埋你。"},{"pid":"01d648c52be4dd95d72f049dfee639480235f090","tid":788710,"uid":3103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:42:00.000Z","msg":"攞嚟賤<br />\n好正路講句<br />\n你男朋友都落到車點解你落唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你真係遲咗囉<br />\n個司機亦都無錯<br />\n閂咗門開車無話一定要比你即刻落車<br />\n再者你打咁大篇野1999<br />\n好心唔好上嚟柒 搏屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P.S:甘你老母呀5P雞 <br />\n         過主啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"20f4fafa175535dc6617041d7e8a3efbb04faf00","tid":788710,"uid":117967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"臭雞"}]}